overview:
FunKarachi.com is one of the largest web portals of Pakistan, it was launched by Tahseen Qureshi on 1st January-2012 to bring revolution in the lives of Pakistanis by giving them a World Class web portal of their own and e-Solutions to their problems. It is meant for Pakistanis and all its categories are being developed taking into consideration the limitations and guidelines set forth of our religion and culture.

It was developed by Funkarachi (Pvt.) Ltd, which is Pakistan’s leading Company By Tahseen Qureshi, thus FunKarachi.com is a live example of the mastery of Funkarachi on cutting edge web technologies.
